      <title>通知顯示，特斯拉將在德州工廠裁員近 2,700 人</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-lay-off-nearly-2700-employees-texas-factory-notice-shows-2024-04-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉表示，將在周二公佈季度業績之前，在德州工廠裁員2,688 名員工，屆時執行長馬斯克預計將概述這家電動車製造商應對需求放緩和利潤下降的戰略。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-lay-off-nearly-2700-employees-texas-factory-notice-shows-2024-04-23/</guid>
